---
title: Soy, Maple and Ginger-Glazed Pork Chops with Stir-Fried Veggies
description: We've added maple syrup to the classic combo of soy and ginger to bring out a hint of caramel when these succulent pork chops are broiled. The caramelization theme continues with mixed veggies stir-fried in a little bit of soy sauce. Rice is plated underneath the pork and veggies to catch all the toasty flavours!
